title: Tim Corley's Web Portfolio & Blog
author: Tim Corley
description: I am a Software Engineer focused on Quality Assurance & Web Development. I have nearly five years of professional experience as a Test Automation Engineer using Python, Selenium, and Appium. I am a constant learner who enjoys exploring technologies by building, breaking, and testing things. In addition to Python & Selenium, I've been focusing lately on React, TypeScript, GraphQL, Node.js, and Postgres. Please take a look around - check out some of my projects, browse my blog posts, and always feel free to get in touch.
